---
// Our Approach section for Construction industry page
---

<section id="approach" class="cre-approach-section">
  <div class="cre-approach-container">
    <span class="section-label">OUR APPROACH FOR CONSTRUCTION</span>
    <h2 class="cre-approach-headline">
      Purpose-built systems for project velocity
    </h2>
    <p class="cre-approach-intro">
      We don't build generic construction software and force it into your workflow. We architect systems specifically for how construction companies operate—from bid to closeout. Every feature is designed to eliminate friction and accelerate project delivery.
    </p>

    <!-- Image Grid -->
    <div class="cre-approach-images-grid">
      <div class="cre-approach-image-item">
        <img 
          src="/logos/intelio-website-pic-dashboard.webp" 
          alt="Project coordination infrastructure"
          class="cre-approach-image"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="cre-approach-image-item">
        <img 
          src="/logos/intelio-dashboard-9.webp" 
          alt="Intelligent automation for construction"
          class="cre-approach-image"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="cre-approach-image-item">
        <img 
          src="/logos/intelio-7.webp" 
          alt="Ownership and control for construction"
          class="cre-approach-image"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text Cards Grid -->
    <div class="cre-approach-cards-grid">
      <div class="cre-approach-card">
        <h3 class="cre-approach-card-title">Project coordination infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="cre-approach-card-description">
          We build unified platforms that connect your entire project—from scheduling through closeout. Every system is designed to reduce coordination overhead, not just store data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cre-approach-card">
        <h3 class="cre-approach-card-title">Intelligent automation</h3>
        <p class="cre-approach-card-description">
          We embed AI and automation into your core workflows—automating crew coordination, tracking budget in real-time, managing changes, and surfacing schedule risks—so your team focuses on building, not administration.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cre-approach-card">
        <h3 class="cre-approach-card-title">Ownership and control</h3>
        <p class="cre-approach-card-description">
          You own the systems we build. No vendor lock-in, no subscription dependencies. We architect for long-term ownership, giving you the flexibility to evolve as your firm grows.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-approach-section {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    padding: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-approach-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-approach-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-approach-intro {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  /* Image Grid */
  .cre-approach-images-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .cre-approach-image-item {
    width: 100%;
    height: 280px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cre-approach-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-approach-image-item:hover .cre-approach-image {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  /* Text Cards Grid */
  .cre-approach-cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cre-approach-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .cre-approach-card-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .cre-approach-card-description {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-approach-images-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .cre-approach-image-item {
      height: 240px;
    }

    .cre-approach-cards-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-approach-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-approach-images-grid {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .cre-approach-image-item {
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>

